title: Pandy Dandy Dudes | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 23
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!


This episode starts off with Chris hitting Sal with a dude and not a babe.....what's the history of the word dude? WHAT UP SON! Dandy meant extremely well dressed man back in the day. We are the athleisure dudes. Shout out Tom Brady! The pandy of 2020 was brutes. Are Drive in movies fun? What will music festivals be post rona? Chris asks for a 40th birthday favor....shout out 1975! Paula Abdul is the best. Sal's Mom has been going wild with her blinds LOL....Sal used to transcribe movies and then act them out for his family. A few good men is a classic movie. We figure out that Chris has never watched a good movie he only watches GARBAGE! What are the top movies of all time? Do you read any of the books you buy? SALS NEW LOOK IS LIT! The babes share a few Mariano Rivera stories. Chris talks about playing in the celebrity all star baseball game. Chris talks about his days workin on Off The Bat on MTV. Sal talks about the Impractical Jokers Movie. It's hard to remember cool moments. Life on the road can get routine. The babes talk local car commericals. Q from Impractical Jokers made a BIG mistake on the baseball field. Sal talks about how it feels to have his own bobble head that looks nothing like him!


Rate us on iTunes!
